That's kind of it.

354
00:24:45,125 --> 00:24:48,416
Like religious scammers
or ghosts who hurt people.

355
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,333
It's not a nice story.

356
00:24:50,416 --> 00:24:52,541
Get to work now. Turn on the computer.

357
00:24:53,125 --> 00:24:54,333
Okay.

358
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:58,791
So you beat people up?
I thought it was only ghosts.

359
00:24:59,583 --> 00:25:02,708
People are good and bad.
Ghosts are no different.

360
00:25:03,333 --> 00:25:07,666
Whether they're humans or ghosts,
