401
00:28:16,416 --> 00:28:18,750
Ugh. You're so sleazy.

402
00:28:19,291 --> 00:28:21,583
I'll never be able
to use a restroom again.

403
00:28:22,708 --> 00:28:25,083
Right. I'm a pervert.

404
00:28:25,916 --> 00:28:29,833
What were you expecting?
That I'd help old ladies cross the road?

405
00:28:29,916 --> 00:28:31,916
- [groans]
- [music stops]

406
00:28:32,958 --> 00:28:35,958
I don't care if you're a pervert.
The gig's up.

407
00:28:36,958 --> 00:28:40,125
I'll give you two choices.
First, you behave.

408
00:28:40,625 --> 00:28:42,291
- Return to the underworld.
- Or?

409
00:28:42,375 --> 00:28:44,708
Or I'll beat you senseless.

410
00:28:45,458 --> 00:28:46,958
My life was meaningless,

411
00:28:47,041 --> 00:28:49,958
