412
00:28:50,041 --> 00:28:51,791
Fine. Do it.

413
00:28:51,875 --> 00:28:53,583
Mister, kill me quick.

414
00:28:53,666 --> 00:28:55,583
Get me to dissipate.

415
00:28:55,666 --> 00:28:58,916
Come on, come on.
Yeah, do it, okay? Okay? [groaning]

416
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:00,708
[comical music continues]

417
00:29:02,541 --> 00:29:05,125
Hold on, hold on! Wait. Just wait. Stop.

418
00:29:05,833 --> 00:29:09,458
Mister, do you think
there's a quicker way than this?

419
00:29:09,541 --> 00:29:11,541
I'll be in pain if I use a pog.

420
00:29:11,625 --> 00:29:14,208
- So just take it--
- Hey, hey. Wait on! Wait on!

421
00:29:17,208 --> 00:29:19,041
Wait! Wait!

422
00:29:19,625 --> 00:29:22,166
I'll… I'll do what you want.

423
00:29:23,208 --> 00:29:24,750
- Hey! No, no!
- [music stops]

424
00:29:24,833 --> 00:29:28,333
Mr. Han! He said
he'll do what you want, okay?

425
00:29:29,333 --> 00:29:30,750
[whimpers]

426
00:29:37,291 --> 00:29:39,791
Where should I go now then?

427
00:29:39,875 --> 00:29:41,291
Not my problem.

428
00:29:41,791 --> 00:29:44,541
You find a place and wait
