448
00:30:41,916 --> 00:30:43,666
It's a win-win for everyone.

449
00:30:43,750 --> 00:30:46,333
She's hot, right?

450
00:30:46,916 --> 00:30:49,041
She is. Quite a good figure, actually.

451
00:30:49,125 --> 00:30:51,375
- Oh, perfect--
- All right. We're going home.

452
00:30:51,458 --> 00:30:52,708
I don't want to go yet.

453
00:30:52,791 --> 00:30:55,666
I want to find my dad
and deal with that ghost.

454
00:30:56,166 --> 00:30:59,125
I told you. There's no smell. It's a fake.

455
00:30:59,208 --> 00:31:01,791
- [funky music playing]
- Hsiao-ming, come with me.

456
00:31:01,875 --> 00:31:03,791
- I'll introduce you.
- Okay. Let's go.

457
00:31:04,708 --> 00:31:05,833
Hey, excuse me.

458
00:31:05,916 --> 00:31:08,750
Could you pull me out, please?
I'm a little stuck here.

459
00:31:08,833 --> 00:31:10,416
Look, I have work to do.

460
00:31:11,791 --> 00:31:14,916
Then if he can't come with me,
